    "body": "Add a `--drop-in <shell>` option to `spack dev-build`. This option will automatically run a `spack build-env <spec> -- <shell>` at the end of a `dev-build`, e.g. to quickly drop-and-devel into a build phase of a package.\r\n\r\nExample usage:\r\n```\r\nspack dev-build --before cmake --drop-in bash openpmd-api@develop\r\n```\r\n\r\n- [x] fix issue in spec\r\n- [x] rebase after #14699",
